data.description: Beautiful New Construction!!! ,Excellent location! Dead end street! Just blocks from SR-82.  You are sure to love !!!  This great room design home has 3 bedrooms 2 baths, Other features of this home include: Traditional eat-in open kitchen , an island with room for seating, Stainless steel kitchen appliances to include: Refrigerator, dishwasher, microwave & range.  Granite countertops in kitchen and baths, Dual sinks in the master bathroom, Porcelain Tile Floor throughout, Master suite features walk-in closet Large. Impact Windows and doors. double door entry. Lanai is relaxing closed with side to side screen. Completely fenced. The property has a relaxing pool and Spa. It has a second kitchen outside. Not located in a flood zone!!! **Great location easy access to Fort Myers, Seconds away from elementary, middle and high schools and the library as well!. Don't let this opportunity pass you by Schedule a Showing today!
